1. What is a Component?

A Component is a reusable piece of UI.

Think of a website:

Navbar
Footer
Sidebar
Login Form
Button

Each can be built as a separate component.

Instead of writing one huge file we divide the UI into small pieces.

2. Why Do We Need Components?

Imagine building Amazon.

Without components:

Navbar code
Navbar code
Navbar code
Navbar code
Navbar code

Repeated everywhere.

Problems:

вќЊ Huge files

вќЊ Hard maintenance

вќЊ Repeated code

вќЊ Difficult debugging

With components:

<Navbar />
<Home />
<Footer />

Much cleaner.

